## Proposed changes

```
for (int32_t partition_id : partition_ids) {
        int64_t low = 0;
        int64_t high = 0;
        RdKafka::ErrorCode err =
                _k_consumer->query_watermark_offsets(_topic, partition_id, &low, &high, 5);
        if (err != RdKafka::ERR_NO_ERROR) {
            std::stringstream ss;
            ss << "failed to get latest offset for partition: " << partition_id
               << ", err: " << RdKafka::err2str(err);
            LOG(WARNING) << ss.str();
            return Status::InternalError(ss.str());
        }
```

fe getInfo timeout is 5s, but in be, the timeout is 5 * partition num.

